    "definitions": [
      {
        "index": 1,
        "gloss": "the system in government offices and business corporations in which draft proposals are prepared by someone in charge of the matter and circulated for collective deliberation and final approval by particular (designated) officials or executives",
        "register": "standard",
        "nuance": null,
        "scenarios": [],
        "sensory_tags": {
          "colors": [],
          "temperature": null,
          "sounds": [],
          "emotions": []
        },
        "collocations": [],
        "examples": {
          "standard": [
            {
              "text": "日本の大企業や官公庁では、稟議制度が意思決定のプロセスとして根強く残っている。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-pro"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "稟議制度は、合意形成を重視する一方で、決定のスピードが遅くなるという欠点も指摘されている。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-pro"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "そのベンチャー企業は、迅速な意思決定のために、従来の稟議制度を廃止した。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-pro"
              }
            }
          ],
